1918  internal static int Utf8Size(string str)
1919  {
1920  if (str == null)
1921  {
1922  return 0;
1923  }
1924 
1925  return str.Length * 4 + 1;
1926  }
1927 
1935  internal static byte[] Utf8Encode(string str, byte[] buffer, int bufferSize)
1936  {
1937  if (str == null)
1938  {
1939  return null;
1940  }
1941 
1942  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str, 0, str.Length, buffer, 0);
1943  buffer[str.Length] = 0; // Null-terminate the string
1944 
1945  return buffer;
1946  }
1947 
1948 
1954  internal static byte[] Utf8EncodeHeap(string str)
1955  {
1956  if (str == null)
1957  {
1958  return null;
1959  }
1960 
1961  int bufferSize = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(str) + 1;
1962  byte[] buffer = new byte[bufferSize];
1963  Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str, 0, str.Length, buffer, 0);
1964  buffer[bufferSize - 1] = 0; // Null-terminate the string
1965 
1966  return buffer;
1967  }
1968 
1969 
1976  public static string UTF8_ToManaged(IntPtr s, bool freePtr = false)
1977  {
1978  if (s == IntPtr.Zero)
1979  {
1980  return null;
1981  }
1982 
1983  byte[] bytes = new byte[0];
1984  int len = 0;
1985  while (Marshal.ReadByte(s, len) != 0)
1986  {
1987  len++;
1988  }
1989 
1990  if (len == 0)
1991  {
1992  return string.Empty;
1993  }
1994 
1995  bytes = new byte[len];
1996  Marshal.Copy(s, bytes, 0, len);
1997  string result = Encoding.UTF8.GetString(bytes);
1998 
1999  if (freePtr)
2000  {
2001  SDL_free(s);
2002  }
2003 
2004  return result;
2005  }

2016  public static uint SDL_FOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => (uint) (a | (b << 8) | (c << 16) | (d << 24));

2471  public static SdlBool SDL_SetHint(string name, string value)
2472  {
2473  int utf8NameBufSize = Utf8Size(name);
2474  byte[] utf8Name = new byte[utf8NameBufSize];
2475 
2476  int utf8ValueBufSize = Utf8Size(value);

2972  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_ShowMessageBox", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
2973  private static extern int INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox([In] ref InternalSdlMessageBoxData messageboxdata, out int buttonid);
2974 
2975 
2981  private static IntPtr INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(string str)
2982  {
2983  if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(str))
2984  {
2985  return IntPtr.Zero;
2986  }
2987 
2988  byte[] bytes = Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(str + '\0');
2989  IntPtr mem = SDL_malloc(bytes.Length);
2990  Marshal.Copy(bytes, 0, mem, bytes.Length);
2991  return mem;
2992  }
2993 
3000  public static int SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref SdlMessageBoxData messageboxdata, out int buttonid)
3001  {
3002  InternalSdlMessageBoxData data = new InternalSdlMessageBoxData
3003  {
3004  flags = messageboxdata.flags,
3005  window = messageboxdata.window,
3006  title = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.title),
3007  message = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.message),
3008  numbuttons = messageboxdata.numbuttons
3009  };
3010 
3011  InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[] buttons = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData[messageboxdata.numbuttons];
3012  IntPtr buttonsPtr = IntPtr.Zero;
3013 
3014  try
3015  {
3016  for (int i = 0; i < messageboxdata.numbuttons; i++)
3017  {
3018  buttons[i] = new InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData
3019  {
3020  flags = messageboxdata.buttons[i].flags,
3021  buttonId = messageboxdata.buttons[i].buttonId,
3022  text = INTERNAL_AllocUTF8(messageboxdata.buttons[i].text)
3023  };
3024  }
3025 
3026  buttonsPtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(buttons.Length * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>());
3027  for (int i = 0; i < buttons.Length; i++)
3028  {
3029  IntPtr buttonPtr = buttonsPtr + i * Marshal.SizeOf<InternalSdlMessageBoxButtonData>();
3030  Marshal.StructureToPtr(buttons[i], buttonPtr, false);
3031  }
3032 
3033  data.buttons = buttonsPtr;
3034 
3035  IntPtr colorSchemePtr = IntPtr.Zero;
3036  if (messageboxdata.colorScheme != null)
3037  {
3038  colorSchemePtr = Marshal.AllocHGlobal(Marshal.SizeOf<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>());
3039  Marshal.StructureToPtr(messageboxdata.colorScheme.Value, colorSchemePtr, false);
3040  }
3041 
3042  int result = INTERNAL_SDL_ShowMessageBox(ref data, out buttonid);
3043 
3044  for (int i = 0; i < messageboxdata.numbuttons; i++)
3045  {
3046  SDL_free(buttons[i].text);
3047  }
3048 
3049  SDL_free(data.message);
3050  SDL_free(data.title);
3051 
3052  if (colorSchemePtr != IntPtr.Zero)
3053  {
3054  Marshal.DestroyStructure<SdlMessageBoxColorScheme>(colorSchemePtr);
3055  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(colorSchemePtr);
3056  }
3057 
3058  return result;
3059  }
3060  finally
3061  {
3062  if (buttonsPtr != IntPtr.Zero)
3063  {
3064  Marshal.FreeHGlobal(buttonsPtr);
3065  }
3066  }
3067  }

6283  public static uint SDL_DEFINE_PIXELFOURCC(byte a, byte b, byte c, byte d) => SDL_FOURCC(a, b, c, d);

6294  public static uint SDL_DEFINE_PIXELFORMAT(
6295  SdlPixelType type,
6296  uint order,
6297  SdlPackedLayout layout,
6298  byte bits,
6299  byte bytes
6300  )
6301  => (uint) (
6302  (1 << 28) |
6303  ((byte) type << 24) |
6304  ((byte) order << 20) |
6305  ((byte) layout << 16) |
6306  (bits << 8) |
6307  bytes
6308  );

6315  public static byte SDL_PIXELFLAG(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 28) & 0x0F);
6316 
6322  public static byte SDL_PIXELTYPE(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 24) & 0x0F);
6323 
6329  public static byte SDL_PIXELORDER(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 20) & 0x0F);
6330 
6336  public static byte SDL_PIXELLAYOUT(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 16) & 0x0F);
6337 
6343  public static byte SDL_BITSPERPIXEL(uint x) => (byte) ((x >> 8) & 0xFF);

6350  public static byte SDL_BYTESPERPIXEL(uint x)
6351  {
6352  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(x))
6353  {
6354  if (x == SdlPixelformatYuy2 ||
6355  x == SdlPixelformatUyvy ||
6356  x == SdlPixelformatYvyu)
6357  {
6358  return 2;
6359  }
6360 
6361  return 1;
6362  }
6363 
6364  return (byte) (x & 0xFF);
6365  }

6372  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_INDEXED(uint format)
6373  {
6374  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6375  {
6376  return false;
6377  }
6378 
6379  SdlPixelType pType =
6380  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6381  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex1 ||
6382  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex4 ||
6383  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeIndex8;
6384  }
6385 
6391  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_PACKED(uint format)
6392  {
6393  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6394  {
6395  return false;
6396  }
6397 
6398  SdlPixelType pType =
6399  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6400  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked8 ||
6401  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked16 ||
6402  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypePacked32;
6403  }
6404 
6410  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ARRAY(uint format)
6411  {
6412  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_FOURCC(format))
6413  {
6414  return false;
6415  }
6416 
6417  SdlPixelType pType =
6418  (SdlPixelType) SDL_PIXELTYPE(format);
6419  return pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu8 ||
6420  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu16 ||
6421  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayu32 ||
6422  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf16 ||
6423  pType == SdlPixelType.SdlPixeltypeArrayf32;
6424  }

6431  public static bool SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ALPHA(uint format)
6432  {
6433  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_PACKED(format))
6434  {
6435  SdlPackedOrder pOrder =
6436  (SdlPackedOrder) SDL_PIXELORDER(format);
6437  return pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderArgb ||
6438  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderRgba ||
6439  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderAbgr ||
6440  pOrder == SdlPackedOrder.SdlPackedorderBgra;
6441  }
6442 
6443  if (SDL_ISPIXELFORMAT_ARRAY(format))
6444  {
6445  SdlArrayOrder aOrder =
6446  (SdlArrayOrder) SDL_PIXELORDER(format);
6447  return aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderArgb ||
6448  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderRgba ||
6449  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderAbgr ||
6450  aOrder == SdlArrayOrder.SdlArrayorderBgra;
6451  }
6452 
6453  return false;
6454  }

7689  [DllImport(NativeLibName, CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]
7690  private static extern SdlBool SDL_GetEventFilter(
7691  out IntPtr filter,
7692  out IntPtr userdata
7693  );
7694 
7701  public static SdlBool SDL_GetEventFilter(
7702  out SdlEventFilter filter,
7703  out IntPtr userdata
7704  )
7705  {
7706  IntPtr result = IntPtr.Zero;
7707  SdlBool retval = SDL_GetEventFilter(out result, out userdata);
7708  if (result != IntPtr.Zero)
7709  {
7710  filter = (SdlEventFilter) Marshal.GetDelegateForFunctionPointer(
7711  result,
7712  typeof(SdlEventFilter)
7713  );
7714  }
7715  else
7716  {
7717  filter = null;
7718  }
7719 
7720  return retval;
7721  }

9167  [DllImport(NativeLibName, EntryPoint = "SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis", CallingConvention = CallingConvention.Cdecl)]

9169  IntPtr gamecontroller,
9170  SdlGameControllerAxis axis
9171  );
9172 
9179  public static SdlGameControllerButtonBind SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
9180  IntPtr gamecontroller,
9181  SdlGameControllerAxis axis
9182  )
9183  {
9184  // This is guaranteed to never be null
9185  InternalSdlGameControllerButtonBind dumb = INTERNAL_SDL_GameControllerGetBindForAxis(
9186  gamecontroller,
9187  axis
9188  );
9189  SdlGameControllerButtonBind result = new SdlGameControllerButtonBind();
9190  result.bindType = (SdlGameControllerBindType) dumb.bindType;
9191  result.value.hat.hat = dumb.unionVal0;
9192  result.value.hat.hat_mask = dumb.unionVal1;
9193  return result;
9194  }
